body:
Star Ocean: First Departure R Remake Announced – PS4 and Nintendo Switch

Star Ocean: First Departure R Remake Announced

Square Enix has finally announced that we’re getting a HD remake of Star Ocean: First Departure R,. The game will be coming to the PlayStation 4 and Nintendo Switch.

For those of you who aren’t aware, Star Ocean: First Departure R is an action RPG developed by tri-Ace and published by Square Enix that released on the Super Famicom in Japan on 19th…
